sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant BookingService
    participant RabbitMQ
    participant PaymentService
    
    Client->>BookingService: 1. Request Checkout
    BookingService->>BookingService: 2. Create Pending Booking
    BookingService->>RabbitMQ: 3. Publish BookingCreatedEvent
    RabbitMQ-->>PaymentService: 4. Consume Event
    PaymentService->>PaymentService: 5. Create Payment Session
    PaymentService->>Client: 6. Return Checkout URL
    
    Client->>PaymentService: 7. Complete Payment (Gateway Webhook)
    PaymentService->>RabbitMQ: 8. Publish PaymentCompletedEvent
    RabbitMQ-->>BookingService: 9. Consume Event
    BookingService->>BookingService: 10. Update Booking = Confirmed
